parcel.description:
# Welcome to Gutter Studio
## A multi-dimensional art and event space. 

Featuring three unique galleries, a multi-level gathering and event space, plus hidden surprises & experiences.

- **Gutter Sam's Studio** - art from [Gutter Sam](https://twitter.com/lifeinthegutter) & the Gutter Studio collection.
- **NXOEED** - art from visual artist and illustrator, [NXOEED](https://nxoeed.carrd.co/)
- **Art Path Gallery** - a curated collection of NFT artists that rotates throughout the year.
